creator: VGR Studios
descriptionHtml:
Marriage photo editor frames app features are inclusive of all the features that one would like to have while editing, ranging from beautiful effects to extravagant overlays and from easiest background changer to simple editing tools, vastest collection of brushes, fonts, splash activity, brightness, contrast, saturation and sharpen adjusters many more. This app definitely is the one with all the essential features to help you create a stunning image even out of scrap.
Features:
1. Crop option: this option allows you to crop the picture to your desired dimensions. Crop here implies free crop. Even rotate the image while your on the crop page if you think its necessary.
2. Cut option: This option helps you to remove the background of any image by drawing a hand-free line around the subject.
3. Erase option: It is used to make your selection more perfect as this option allows you to remove those unwanted areas by selecting those areas.
4. Background or Frame: Here you can select what to be selected, either it be background or frame based on your requirement. We recommend you to go for backgrounds if you are willing to take time and go for full fledge editing process, whereas frames are for quick fire editing. Also, after opting out of two, choose the desired one out of the collection of backgrounds or frames that we have.
5. Stickers: Realistic stickers of rings, flowers and balloons are kept for use just in case you think to use them to make your wonderful edits.
6.Text option: add different text styles, colors and shadows for your text to make your edit unique and also make them speak out of the rest.
7.Effects: Unique effects that bring up the colors of your images to live are fitted with an opacity bar so that you can decide which certain amount would be perfect for your image.
8. Overlays: Brilliant overlays that can create bokeh out of nothing also come with an opacity bar that can adjust the opacity of the overlays that are given to you.
9. Fit option: Image fit that allows you to resize your images to standard dimensions without losing a part of an image.
10. Blur: Blur here can be implied either with the help of a shape tool or by hand, i.e. by brush.
11. Splash: with this feature you can make monochrome of selected parts of an image.
12. Save: for saving your beautiful edits.
13. Share: for sharing of your edits to your friends on any social media platforms.
